## Requirements
- Wrap the body of every control statement in `{}` even if single-line
- No single-line `if (x) doSomething()` patterns
- Auto-fixable by ESLint `curly: "all"`

## Examples
<example>
if (ready) {
  start();
}
</example>

<example type="invalid">
if (ready) start();
</example>

